# Agentic Code - Prompt Orchestrator

**ğŸ†“ 100% FREE - Local-first, governed multi-model agentic coding pipeline**

A CLI tool that orchestrates governed, multi-agent coding workflows using **prompt generation** instead of API calls. Zero cost, maximum control.

---

## ğŸ¯ What Makes This Different

### **Traditional AI Coding Tools:**
- âŒ Single AI does everything (plan, code, verify)
- âŒ Black-box execution (can't see prompts)
- âŒ API costs ($0.10-0.50 per task)
- âŒ No separation of duties
- âŒ Limited governance

### **Agentic Code (Prompt Orchestrator):**
- âœ… **Separation of duties** - Different AI models for different roles
- âœ… **100% transparent** - See and edit every prompt
- âœ… **Zero cost** - Uses free tools (Claude Code CLI, Cursor, Gemini)
- âœ… **Human-in-the-loop** - Review and approve every step
- âœ… **Complete audit trail** - Every decision documented
- âœ… **No API keys** - Works with tools you already have

